{"tid":567050,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[Fiona JJ]鍾意 給十年後的我 定 Dear Fiona多啲？","createTime":"2018-02-20T13:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T01:48:16.000Z","uid":34701,"like":10,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"694604e6a8fb29d4b63d9cc692ca86d84ce86170","tid":567050,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"由Fiona出道開始就已經鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而呢兩首歌都係想同自己表達一啲訊息/諗法，歌詞都好有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為本身都鍾意YUI嘅關係，所以特別鍾意Dear Fiona嘅曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但給十年後的我又有一種勿忘初衷嘅感覺，人越大聽落就越有共鳴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩首都好正，你哋會點揀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：給十年後的我<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：Dear Fiona"},{"pid":"caccf16e615ea319b0dd3e6335ac342145e6c122","tid":567050,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7b51646a0daf61427c4ed5a01d634f3d2d3f8a","tid":567050,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f50cad2f1ca1aeb54ef00dca8d5b1f2ec9707e7","tid":567050,"uid":159444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:47:29.000Z","msg":"前者正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皮已正"},{"pid